{
  "page": "Manse",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1c/Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG/350px-Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG\" width=\"350\" height=\"228\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1c/Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG/525px-Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG 1.5x, /images/1/1c/Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Folko_Streese_pentoshi_manor.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentoshi</a> Manor, by Folko Streese © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the King-Beyond-the-Wall, see <a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a>.</div>\n<p>A <b>manse</b> is a large house similar to a mansion or manor. Manses are frequently owned by the wealthy,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthree_heads_had_the_dragon_-_governance_under_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthree_heads_had_the_dragon_-_governance_under_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> such as by merchants<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> in cities,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> though they can also be found in the countryside.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> Manses can be fortified and found within walled estates.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragon</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Aenys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenys I Targaryen\">Aenys I Targaryen</a> resided at a manse atop <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya%27s_Hill\" title=\"Visenya&#39;s Hill\">Visenya's Hill</a> during construction of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Rego_Draz\" title=\"Rego Draz\">Rego Draz</a> owned a manse on the <a href=\"/index.php/Street_of_Silk\" title=\"Street of Silk\">Street of Silk</a> near the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a> and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Laena_Velaryon\" title=\"Laena Velaryon\">Laena Velaryon</a> settled in a manse outside <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a> owned by a <a href=\"/index.php/Magister\" title=\"Magister\">magister</a> while waiting for Laena to give birth to <a href=\"/index.php/Baela_Targaryen\" title=\"Baela Targaryen\">Baela</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaena_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Daemon)\" title=\"Rhaena Targaryen (daughter of Daemon)\">Rhaena Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabheirs_of_the_draogn_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_draogn_-_a_question_of_succession.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Bartimos_Celtigar\" title=\"Bartimos Celtigar\">Bartimos Celtigar</a> was slain in his manse amid the <a href=\"/index.php/Riot_of_King%27s_Landing_(Dance_of_the_Dragons)\" title=\"Riot of King&#39;s Landing (Dance of the Dragons)\">riot of King's Landing</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys II Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> stayed at the manse of <a href=\"/index.php/Bambarro_Bazanne\" title=\"Bambarro Bazanne\">Bambarro Bazanne</a> while a captive in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Marilda_of_Hull\" title=\"Marilda of Hull\">Marilda of Hull</a> built a palatial manse at <a href=\"/index.php/Hull\" title=\"Hull\">Hull</a> which <a href=\"/index.php/Mushroom\" title=\"Mushroom\">Mushroom</a> dubbed the <a href=\"/index.php/Mouse_House\" title=\"Mouse House\">Mouse House</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After the passing of <a href=\"/index.php/Vogarro\" title=\"Vogarro\">Vogarro</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Widow_of_the_waterfront\" title=\"Widow of the waterfront\">his widow</a> had to sell his manse inside the <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Wall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Black Wall\">Black Wall</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> because freedmen are not allowed inside.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_15-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-15\">&#91;15&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a> was fighting as a <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a>, his wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Lynesse_Hightower\" title=\"Lynesse Hightower\">Lynesse Hightower</a>, moved into <a href=\"/index.php/Tregar_Ormollen\" title=\"Tregar Ormollen\">Tregar Ormollen</a>'s manse in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_16-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-16\">&#91;16&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>Ghiscari inter their honored dead in crypts below their manses.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_17-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd71.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-17\">&#91;17&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Shae%27s_ManseFM.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/27/Shae%27s_ManseFM.png/350px-Shae%27s_ManseFM.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"222\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/27/Shae%27s_ManseFM.png/525px-Shae%27s_ManseFM.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/27/Shae%27s_ManseFM.png/700px-Shae%27s_ManseFM.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Shae%27s_ManseFM.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Manse_near_the_Iron_Gate\" title=\"Manse near the Iron Gate\">Shae's manse</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>, by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> are guests at <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">the manse</a> of Magister <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> The siblings then reside at <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo%27s_manse\" title=\"Drogo&#39;s manse\">Drogo's manse</a> before <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Drogo_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Drogo and Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys's wedding</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_18-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-18\">&#91;18&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenerys sees manses of woven grass as large as castles in <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> settles his mistress, <a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">Shae</a>, in the <a href=\"/index.php/Manse_near_the_Iron_Gate\" title=\"Manse near the Iron Gate\">manse near the Iron Gate</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_19-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-19\">&#91;19&#93;</a></sup> A manse owned by a <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">goldsmith</a> is burned down during the <a href=\"/index.php/Riots_in_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Riots in King&#39;s Landing\">riots in King's Landing</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_20-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-20\">&#91;20&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenerys stays at <a href=\"/index.php/Xaro%27s_home\" title=\"Xaro&#39;s home\">the manse</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a>, finding it vastly larger than Illyrio's manse.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_21-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-21\">&#91;21&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragon\"><i>A Dance with Dragon</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragon\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Varys\" title=\"Varys\">Varys</a> has Tyrion smuggled from <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> to Illyrio's home in Pentos.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_22-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-22\">&#91;22&#93;</a></sup> Tyrion sees the ruins of what might have been a huge stone manse while traveling in the countryside between Pentos and <a href=\"/index.php/Ghoyan_Drohe\" title=\"Ghoyan Drohe\">Ghoyan Drohe</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Downstream, below the black marble walls and arched windows of the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a>, the manses of the pious clustered like children gathered round the feet of an old dowager.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_23-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-23\">&#91;23&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_(novice)\" title=\"Pate (novice)\">Pate</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>One voyage to the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a> and we'll be as rich as <a href=\"/index.php/Gods\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gods\">gods</a>. We can have a manse in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> or one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_the_Maid\" title=\"Qarl the Maid\">Qarl the Maid</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Asha_Greyjoy\" title=\"Asha Greyjoy\">Asha Greyjoy</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Manse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthree_heads_had_the_dragon_-_governance_under_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthree_heads_had_the_dragon_-_governance_under_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Three Heads Had the Dragon - Governance Under King Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_triumphant.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Triumphant.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - Rhaenyra Overthrown.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 18\">Chapter 18</a>, Catelyn IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">5.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\">5.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_36\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 36\">Chapter 36</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">6.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\">6.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_26\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 26\">Chapter 26</a>, The Wayward Bride.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\">7.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd8.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\">7.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_8\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\">8.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot3.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\">8.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_3\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 3\">Chapter 3</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_policy.2C_progeny.2C_and_pain.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Jaehaerys and Alysanne - Policy, Progeny, and Pain.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabheirs_of_the_draogn_-_a_question